---
title: Spiced Pork with Creamy Lentils and Nigella Chapatis
description: André has whipped up this great winter warmer to get you through the darkest of evenings. The fiery Malay spiced pork is tempered with creamy, filling lentils. He has even topped it off with super quick nigella seed flavoured chapatis - a taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-pork-with-creamy-lentils-08e247cc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spiced-pork-with-creamy-lentils-67a392f8.pdf
